      "created_at": "2025-06-17T13:46:00.154Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Hi there are many things that could be going on here.  My guess is you need to go to connections and click on your device and click \u201ccontrollable\u201d but if you send me a screenshot of when you are pedalling that would help.  Bluetooth interference can cause issues like this.   There are many possibilities.  Let me know if you still have problems.</p>",
