      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/b/3da27b/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2025-06-17T20:42:41.888Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Heya - Thanks for responding. I\u2019ve just had a play around with some settings. I wasn\u2019t able to find the \u201ccontrollable\u201d setting when looking at my connected devices (see screenshot below).</p>\n<p>When playing around today I had the same issue. Just couldn\u2019t get the required resistance. However I came out of the exercise &amp; tried the quick start. Still had the issue initially but I switched mode from ERG to Resistance &amp; immediately felt the resistance kick in. - I then stopped this exercise, went back into the planned workout &amp; it seemed to be working fine. Much more stable &amp; could easily hit the required power at low RPM.</p>\n<p>I\u2019ll have another play around tomorrow &amp; see if regularly doing this seems to fix things. A few extra screenshots below showing different conditions.</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/2X/2/2630e5258da9bc8022b65961f3052c1249824286.png\" data-download-href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/2630e5258da9bc8022b65961f3052c1249824286\" title=\"Screenshot_20250617-212540\"><img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/2/2630e5258da9bc8022b65961f3052c1249824286_2_222x499.png\" alt=\"Screenshot_20250617-212540\" data-base62-sha1=\"5rQTS2qtNNDcIvMKsfCBJUUMG0u\" width=\"222\" height=\"499\" srcset=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/2/2630e5258da9bc8022b65961f3052c1249824286_2_222x499.png, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/2/2630e5258da9bc8022b65961f3052c1249824286_2_333x748.png 1.5x, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/2/2630e5258da9bc8022b65961f3052c1249824286_2_444x998.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"203039\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot_20250617-2125